THEY STEAL FROM YOUR CAR! DO NOT RESERVE PARKING THERE!

I booked 199 Water Street Garage LLC located on 147 John St. New York, NY through Spothero for $41.67, just for 2 HOURS yesterday, September 4th, 2023!

It’s VALET parking and someone who works there STOLE $5 worth of Quarters from the center console of my car! I need/use those quarters for parking meters and some fool didn’t think I would notice! I had proof, because I took a photo of my quarters, before I left my car with an attendant!!! I’m NOT rich, I I NEED MY MONEY! I use QUARTERS EVERY DAY FOR METERS!

DO NOT PURCHASE PARKING HERE! YOUR BELONGINGS ARE NOT SAFE! I called the cops to come with me to confront them and was able to file a Police Report and will follow up! THEY HAVE NO RIGHT TO STEAL ANYTHING FROM MY CAR! VALET PARKING IS SUPPOSED TO JUST PARK YOUR CAR, AND NOT OPEN OTHER COMPARTMENTS OF THE CAR! I WAS FURIOUS! THIS IS NO TREASURE HUNT? THEY NEED TO HIRE NEW PEOPLE AND DO THROUGH CRIMINAL BACKGROUND CHECKS!

THIS PERSON PROBABLY STOLE FROM LOADS OF PEOPLE! THAT’S NOT FAIR! JUSTICE NEEDS TO BE SERVED! THE PERSON NEEDS TO GET FIRED!
